data.description: Open House Sunday 9-17 from 12pm-4pm. Check out this beautiful 3 bed 2 bath home.  Great open floor concept featuring high ceilings, granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances including the fridge. Vinyl plank flooring in the entryway, kitchen, living and dinning room area and carpet in the bedrooms. Sprinkler system front and back. Prime location with easy access to 1604 and IH10 or IH35.  This home is only 2 years old and still in like new condition.
